; Coverage for history.cc line 488: last_target reassignment in multi-hop path
; A->B->C->D chain: 10 A * 2 B/A * 3 C/B * 4 D/C = 240 D
; Each hop changes last_target, exercising both branches of the assignment

P 2024/01/01 A 2 B
P 2024/01/01 B 3 C
P 2024/01/01 C 4 D

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses:Test    10 A
    Assets:Cash

test bal --market --exchange D --now 2024/02/01 Expenses
                D240  Expenses:Test
end test
